data.description: SPECTACULAR, BEAUTIFULLY UPDATED POOL HOME IN PLANTATION BAY AVAILABLE! This 2266 square foot, 3 bed, 2 bath, 2 car garage home has had some massive updates! New roof was installed in February 2020, new appliances and faux wood blinds installed 2023, fabulous gourmet kitchen with an abundance of cabinets features a large, 10 foot granite breakfast bar, master and guest bath beautifully renovated, resurfaced pool, vinyl flooring, and the list goes on! Large windows throughout the Florida room allows for lots of natural light and fantastic views of the pool. The dining and family room feature a soaring cathedral ceiling which also overlooks the pool as you relax. The convenient split plan has the large tranquil master bedroom with double french doors, that overlooks the pool through the Florida room as well. The spacious master bathroom offers a walk-in shower with bench as well as dual sinks for convenience. The two guest bedrooms offer ample space for your guests, an office or storage. Outside you find the crystal clear pool for your family and friends get togethers on hot Florida days! Come live the Plantation Bay lifestyle!! Call today to schedule your appointment to view! All Realtor Information and Measurements Intended to be Accurate but not Guaranteed. Buyer and Buyers Agent to verify all Property uses including Zoned Schools, HOA, Pets, Measurements, Lease Restrictions and Zoning as well as any other Intended Uses. ***
